text: Madqooqik oobisnaamah aayat aka aayatih aracat nabiddile waqdi, Yalli isi naqoosah meqeemiy kayri keenik edde yaniy oobisa yaaxigeh, koros : Mucammadow zafe cagalah atu Yalli axce weem Yallal diraabah ginnaasite kinnito itte, Nabii Mucammadow ≈ùafe usun kah iyyan inna hinnay keenik maggo mari sinni Rabbih madqooqi ma yaaxiga
